{"article_id":"c6R9ii1FHVpp3OuQ","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Democrats Want FBI To Investigate Kavanaugh Allegations .","depth":3},{"id":1,"text":"It Likely Wo n't","depth":3},{"id":2,"text":"When Senate Judiciary Committee Chairman Chuck Grassley , a Republican from Iowa , announced a hearing for next Monday","depth":5},{"id":3,"text":"to air a decades-old sexual-assault allegation against Supreme Court nominee Brett Kavanaugh ,","depth":5},{"id":4,"text":"it did n't end the debate","depth":5},{"id":5,"text":"over how the Senate should handle the charges .","depth":5},{"id":6,"text":"Democrats are calling for a full FBI investigation of the allegation before a hearing ,","depth":5},{"id":7,"text":"saying","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"Monday is too soon .","depth":6},{"id":9,"text":"`` I 'd have the professionals go in there ,","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"seek corroborating evidence ,","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"talk to the people involved ,","depth":10},{"id":12,"text":"certainly talk to the third person","depth":11},{"id":13,"text":"who","depth":13},{"id":14,"text":"they claimed","depth":13},{"id":15,"text":"was there ,","depth":12},{"id":16,"text":"and that has n't been done , ''","depth":9},{"id":17,"text":"Democratic Sen. Patrick Leahy of Vermont , a longtime member of the Judiciary Committee and a former chairman , told NPR 's Morning Edition .","depth":6},{"id":18,"text":"`` This might take a week or two to get all of this together ,","depth":6},{"id":19,"text":"but what difference does one or two weeks make","depth":7},{"id":20,"text":"when you 're talking about a lifetime appointment . ''","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"Politics","depth":2},{"id":22,"text":"Kavanaugh And His Accuser To Appear Before Senate Judiciary Committee","depth":3},{"id":23,"text":"Kavanaugh And His Accuser To Appear Before Senate Judiciary Committee","depth":6},{"id":24,"text":"Listen · 5:51 5:51","depth":6},{"id":25,"text":"Republicans and the Trump White House argue","depth":7},{"id":26,"text":"that is n't the FBI 's role .","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"The Justice Department seems to agree .","depth":7},{"id":28,"text":"In a statement , a Justice Department spokeswoman said","depth":10},{"id":29,"text":"the FBI","depth":13},{"id":30,"text":"- which has added a letter from Christine Blasey Ford to Kavanaugh 's already completed background report file -","depth":13},{"id":31,"text":"had already done all","depth":13},{"id":32,"text":"it was going to do ,","depth":13},{"id":33,"text":"because `` the allegation does not involve any potential federal crime . ''","depth":11},{"id":34,"text":"`` The FBI does not make any judgment about the credibility or significance of any allegation , ''","depth":12},{"id":35,"text":"the statement reads .","depth":12},{"id":36,"text":"`` The purpose of a background investigation is to determine","depth":14},{"id":37,"text":"whether the nominee could pose a risk to the national security of the United States .","depth":14},{"id":38,"text":"The allegation does not involve any potential federal crime .","depth":13},{"id":39,"text":"The FBI 's role in such matters is to provide information for the use of the decision makers . ''","depth":12},{"id":40,"text":"Grassley was more definitive in an interview with conservative radio host Hugh Hewitt Tuesday morning .","depth":10},{"id":41,"text":"`` The FBI investigation of Judge Kavanaugh is closed , ''","depth":10},{"id":42,"text":"he said .","depth":10},{"id":43,"text":"`` The FBI is not doing any further investigation . ''","depth":9},{"id":44,"text":"Blasey Ford has accused Kavanaugh of a sexual attack","depth":7},{"id":45,"text":"when they were both in high school .","depth":7},{"id":46,"text":"She sent a letter to her congresswoman , Rep. Anna Eshoo , in July ,","depth":10},{"id":47,"text":"which made its way to Sen. Dianne Feinstein , a Democrat from California and ranking member of the Judiciary Committee .","depth":10},{"id":48,"text":"Blasey Ford asked for confidentiality ,","depth":13},{"id":49,"text":"and the allegation was not made public","depth":13},{"id":50,"text":"- until this past weekend .","depth":12},{"id":51,"text":"That 's when she came forward for the first time publicly in an interview with The Washington Post .","depth":11},{"id":52,"text":"She detailed her memories of the incident ,","depth":11},{"id":53,"text":"saying","depth":12},{"id":54,"text":"that Kavanaugh pulled her into a bedroom along with another boy ,","depth":13},{"id":55,"text":"then allegedly groped her ,","depth":14},{"id":56,"text":"trying to remove her clothing ,","depth":15},{"id":57,"text":"and put his hand over her mouth","depth":16},{"id":58,"text":"to muffle her screams .","depth":16},{"id":59,"text":"Kavanaugh responded through the White House with a categorical denial .","depth":9},{"id":60,"text":"`` This is a completely false allegation , ''","depth":12},{"id":61,"text":"he said .","depth":12},{"id":62,"text":"`` I have never done anything like what the accuser describes","depth":13},{"id":63,"text":"- to her or to anyone .","depth":13},{"id":64,"text":"Because this never happened ,","depth":13},{"id":65,"text":"I had no idea","depth":15},{"id":66,"text":"who was making this accusation","depth":15},{"id":67,"text":"until she identified herself yesterday .","depth":14},{"id":68,"text":"I am willing to talk to the Senate Judiciary Committee in any way","depth":12},{"id":69,"text":"the Committee deems appropriate","depth":12},{"id":70,"text":"to refute this false allegation , from 36 years ago ,","depth":12},{"id":71,"text":"and defend my integrity . ''","depth":12},{"id":72,"text":"He will do that in a scheduled hearing Monday , in what Democrats worry","depth":9},{"id":73,"text":"will be a replay of another","depth":9},{"id":74,"text":"he-said , she-said exercise in 1991","depth":9},{"id":75,"text":"when Anita Hill came forward with sexual harassment allegations against then-Supreme Court nominee Clarence Thomas .","depth":9},{"id":76,"text":"Democrats complained","depth":10},{"id":77,"text":"that there was not a thorough FBI investigation of the allegations","depth":12},{"id":78,"text":"that took place ,","depth":12},{"id":79,"text":"and no major witnesses other than Hill and Thomas","depth":12},{"id":80,"text":"who were called .","depth":12},{"id":81,"text":"Monday 's planned hearing seems to be following a similar pattern .","depth":9},{"id":82,"text":"Grassley told Hewitt Tuesday","depth":12},{"id":83,"text":"that , `` Yes , '' there will only be two witnesses Monday .","depth":12},{"id":84,"text":"`` We 've got two people involved , ''","depth":13},{"id":85,"text":"Grassley said ,","depth":13},{"id":86,"text":"`` and two people ought to be able to present their stories","depth":13},{"id":87,"text":"and then we 'll have to be the jury . ''","depth":13},{"id":88,"text":"Grassley added ,","depth":11},{"id":89,"text":"`` Accusers deserve to be heard","depth":13},{"id":90,"text":"and , after they 're heard","depth":14},{"id":91,"text":"and we also have a responsibility","depth":15},{"id":92,"text":"to hear Judge Kavanaugh ,","depth":15},{"id":93,"text":"and I want to hear from Dr. Ford ,","depth":13},{"id":94,"text":"and she deserves to be heard ,","depth":14},{"id":95,"text":"because these are serious accusations . ''","depth":14},{"id":96,"text":"Grassley said","depth":10},{"id":97,"text":"it is n't even 100 percent certain at this point","depth":12},{"id":98,"text":"whether Ford or Kavanaugh will testify first ,","depth":12},{"id":99,"text":"though he is inclined to have Ford go first .","depth":11},{"id":100,"text":"On Morning Edition Tuesday , Leahy suggested","depth":11},{"id":101,"text":"that another man","depth":13},{"id":102,"text":"who was allegedly in the room at the time of the encounter","depth":13},{"id":103,"text":"be called before the committee .","depth":12},{"id":104,"text":"There were other potential witnesses","depth":12},{"id":105,"text":"who came forward before the Hill-Thomas hearings ,","depth":12},{"id":106,"text":"and then-Chairman Joe Biden declined to let them testify , something","depth":12},{"id":107,"text":"he now has said publicly","depth":13},{"id":108,"text":"he regrets .","depth":13},{"id":109,"text":"Democrats argue","depth":13},{"id":110,"text":"that other witnesses could provide context","depth":14},{"id":111,"text":"and verify or refute parts of the stories","depth":15},{"id":112,"text":"that either person tells .","depth":15},{"id":113,"text":"For example , a friend and neighbor of Blasey Ford 's told the San Jose Mercury News","depth":14},{"id":114,"text":"that Blasey Ford told her of the incident in 2017","depth":15},{"id":115,"text":"before Kavanaugh was nominated .","depth":15},{"id":116,"text":"`` It 's been difficult for Blasey Ford over the years ,","depth":15},{"id":117,"text":"[ Blasey Ford ] told [ Rebecca ] White ,","depth":15},{"id":118,"text":"because the judge 's name would come up as ' a super powerful guy","depth":15},{"id":119,"text":"and he might be a contender for a Supreme Court position one day . ' ``","depth":15},{"id":120,"text":"Grassley told Hewitt","depth":15},{"id":121,"text":"that he has not heard from Blasey Ford yet ,","depth":15},{"id":122,"text":"saying","depth":15},{"id":123,"text":"the committee has reached out to her .","depth":15},{"id":124,"text":"`` We still have n't heard from Dr. Ford ,","depth":15},{"id":125,"text":"so do they want to have the hearing or not ? ''","depth":15},{"id":126,"text":"Grassley said .","depth":14},{"id":127,"text":"Blasey Ford 's attorneys told NPR 's Morning Edition and other outlets","depth":13},{"id":128,"text":"that Ford is willing to testify .","depth":13},{"id":129,"text":"Grassley told Hewitt","depth":12},{"id":130,"text":"he hoped","depth":13},{"id":131,"text":"the hearing would n't devolve into a circuslike atmosphere .","depth":13},{"id":132,"text":"The days of Kavanaugh confirmation hearings were often interrupted by protesters ,","depth":13},{"id":133,"text":"and Republicans accused Democrats","depth":15},{"id":134,"text":"- especially those possible 2020 presidential candidates -","depth":15},{"id":135,"text":"of grandstanding .","depth":14},{"id":136,"text":"`` I 'd like to see 21 members of our committee listen patiently to both witnesses , ''","depth":14},{"id":137,"text":"Grassley said ,","depth":14},{"id":138,"text":"`` and kind of act like a jury","depth":14},{"id":139,"text":"and then wait","depth":17},{"id":140,"text":"until you hear all the evidence ,","depth":17},{"id":141,"text":"and then make your mind up afterwards .","depth":16},{"id":142,"text":"And I 'm going to be respectful ,","depth":16},{"id":143,"text":"and I hope","depth":17},{"id":144,"text":"my colleagues will be too . ''","depth":17},{"id":145,"text":"Grassley also could n't answer","depth":11},{"id":146,"text":"whether each senator will get one or two rounds of questions .","depth":11},{"id":147,"text":"He said","depth":11},{"id":148,"text":"that has n't been worked out","depth":13},{"id":149,"text":"and pointed to the Democrats ,","depth":13},{"id":150,"text":"noting","depth":13},{"id":151,"text":"that there has n't been a lot of cooperation from Democratic staff .","depth":13},{"id":152,"text":"Hewitt asked","depth":11},{"id":153,"text":"whether there was any thought","depth":12},{"id":154,"text":"of having a female lawyer or someone like former Republican Sen. Kelly Ayotte of New Hampshire come in","depth":14},{"id":155,"text":"to do the questioning","depth":14},{"id":156,"text":"since there are no Republican women on the Judiciary Comittee .","depth":13},{"id":157,"text":"`` You 're raising legitimate questions","depth":13},{"id":158,"text":"that are still on our mind , ''","depth":13},{"id":159,"text":"Grassley said ,","depth":12},{"id":160,"text":"`` and so these details are still being worked out . ''","depth":11},{"id":161,"text":"All","depth":10},{"id":162,"text":"that 's certain at the moment","depth":10},{"id":163,"text":"is that a hearing is scheduled for Monday ,","depth":9},{"id":164,"text":"and that both Kavanaugh and Blasey Ford have been invited","depth":9},{"id":165,"text":"and have expressed an openness","depth":10},{"id":166,"text":"to participating","depth":11},{"id":167,"text":"to publicly tell their side of the story .","depth":11},{"id":168,"text":"For Republicans ,","depth":11},{"id":169,"text":"who wanted Kavanaugh confirmed in time for the start of the new Supreme Court session","depth":12},{"id":170,"text":"beginning Oct. 1 ,","depth":12},{"id":171,"text":"a week or two would throw that timeline off .","depth":10},{"id":172,"text":"More important , Republicans want him confirmed before November 's elections in the off chance","depth":11},{"id":173,"text":"that Democrats take control of the Senate .","depth":11},{"id":174,"text":"Then again , this new allegation has already cast a massive shadow over Kavanaugh 's nomination .","depth":10},{"id":175,"text":"Kavanaugh 's supporters in the Senate and the White House question Democrats ' motives ,","depth":10},{"id":176,"text":"suggesting","depth":11},{"id":177,"text":"all they really want","depth":12},{"id":178,"text":"is to delay a confirmation vote .","depth":12},{"id":179,"text":"`` He was n't going to vote for Brett Kavanaugh to be on the Supreme Court in the first place , ''","depth":12},{"id":180,"text":"Kellyanne Conway , counselor to the president , said of Leahy ,","depth":13},{"id":181,"text":"who appeared before her on the PBS NewsHour Monday night .","depth":13},{"id":182,"text":"`` A lot of people in the Senate were n't going to vote for him anyway . ''","depth":11},{"id":183,"text":"Still , Conway and other Republicans are going out of their way","depth":12},{"id":184,"text":"to say","depth":13},{"id":185,"text":"they want Ford and Kavanaugh to be heard .","depth":13},{"id":186,"text":"`` It 's good to hear from both the accuser and the accused here , ''","depth":13},{"id":187,"text":"Conway said ,","depth":13},{"id":188,"text":"`` and allow the Senate to weigh what they learn in those exchanges , along with the mountain of other testimonial evidence and other statements of support and endorsements of Brett Kavanaugh by the women","depth":13},{"id":189,"text":"he 's known all throughout his life . ''","depth":13}],"relations":[{"parent":379,"left":210,"right":378,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":210,"left":191,"right":209,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":191,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":209,"left":194,"right":208,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":194,"left":192,"right":193,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":192,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":193,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":208,"left":196,"right":207,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":196,"left":6,"right":195,"relation":"condition","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":195,"left":7,"right":8,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":207,"left":204,"right":206,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":204,"left":203,"right":17,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":203,"left":9,"right":202,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":202,"left":10,"right":201,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":201,"left":200,"right":16,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":200,"left":11,"right":199,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":199,"left":12,"right":198,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":198,"left":197,"right":15,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":197,"left":13,"right":14,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":206,"left":18,"right":205,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":205,"left":19,"right":20,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":378,"left":21,"right"